        <infon key="n">3</infon>
        <offset>203</offset>
        <text>Iron thus plays an important role in the carbon cycle, and changes in its supply to the surface ocean may have had a significant effect on atmospheric carbon dioxide concentrations over glacial-interglacial cycles.
</text>
