      <sentence>
        <infon key="n">7</infon>
        <offset>941</offset>
        <text>We found that a large phytoplankton bloom over the Kerguelen plateau in the Southern Ocean was sustained by the supply of iron and major nutrients to surface waters from iron-rich deep water below.
</text>
